rows.label: tev072201_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Run'tonam if anything is troubling her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072201_MSG0001
rows.name:
Since the distant past, we weak-bodied Orphe have
been guided by our Ovah.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072201_MSG0002
rows.name:
We evaded enemies, evolved, and survived to the
present day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072201_MSG0003
rows.name:
I know this merely by feeling that which flows through
this body of mine as well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072201_MSG0004
rows.name:
But at times I wonder if it will truly lead us to the
correct path.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072201_MSG0005
rows.name:
It is not true of us all, but apparently some betaforms
harbor doubts about the Ovah.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072201_MSG0010
rows.name:
Ever since I was split off from On'tonam, I have felt an
overpowering sensation of being...out of place.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072201_MSG0011
rows.name:
I do not understand its source, and I feel strongly that
so long as I continue on the way I have, I never will.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072201_MSG0012
rows.name:
My Ovah provides me no insight, and none of the
other Orpheans I've spoken to understand my plight.[ST:wait ]
